    "When we face new task scenarios, what we need to consider is to follow relevant protocols to develop new templates to support new models (detailed in Section 5.2).",
    "Usage of EduStudio run_edustudioThe code example of running a model is illustrated in Fig. 6.",
    "The function is the entry point for the whole experimental process including running an existing model and running a customized model.",
    "Running existing models run_edustudio cls clses emb_size modeltpl_c f g_dict MyModelTo run an existing model, we need to specify at least the dataset name (i.e., dataset parameter in) and template name in each step in the algorithm workflow (i.e., the or key in corresponding parameter dictionary).",
    "The corresponding templates of models are detailed in online Reference Table."
